# Smart NGO Resource Platform — Full Context Summary (Updated 2026-06-06)

## Project Overview

A full-stack monorepo web platform connecting **citizens** with **NGOs**. Citizens submit resource requests and make donations (goods/money). NGOs review requests, manage volunteers, track resources, and manage their financial accounts. A Super Admin oversees the entire platform.

