| `ResourceAllocation` | id, resourceId (→Resource RESTRICT), requestId (→Request CASCADE), ngoId, quantity (Float), notes?, allocatedBy | deducts from Resource.quantity |
| `Notification` | id, userId, type, title, body, isRead (default false) | @@index([userId, isRead]) |
| `RequestStatusLog` | id, requestId, status, changedBy, note? | audit trail for status changes |
| `Comment` | id, requestId, authorId, body (Text) | any authenticated user can comment |
| `ResourceDonation` | id, citizenId, ngoId, itemName, category, quantity (Float), unit?, description?, status (default "PENDING"), ngoNote?, respondedAt? | citizen offers goods to NGO |
| `MoneyDonation` | id, citizenId, ngoId, amount (Float), message?, status (default "COMPLETED") | citizen donates money; auto-updates NGOAccount |
